items.name: PC-98 Lora
items.description:
Trained on anything v3.1 with ~2.3k images from old japanese games (mostly pc-98, but also pc-88, pc engine and X68000). This lora has a heavy female bias due to the training data (meaning your 1boys will probably not look very masculine! You can try tags such as man instead to counterbalance this somewhat.)

The training tags were stripped of extra "quality control" tags like dithering, jaggy lines, oekaki, retro style, etc. You can add them to your prompt or negative prompt, but mostly the result hinges on including the keyword mentioned above. Also works with both "plaintext" and underscored tags (Ex: dutch angle vs dutch_angle - trained on both just in case).

Now with 3 levels!

Strong - Very in line with the pc-98 concept. It has Dithering, Jaggy lines, etc that emulate the style as much as possible. (However, be aware it IS strong so some experimentation might be needed when it comes to weighting it.) Recommended weight: 0.7-1.

Medium - still in line with the concept, albeit it eases up on the artifacts like dithering, jaggy lines, etc. It's style falls roughly inbetween the light and strong versions. Some tinkering might still be required but overall works "easier" and doesn't require overt wrestling to get alright results. Recommended weight: 0.8-1.

Light - Since this is quite a light version of the original, it'd describe it's style more like a "retro look" than specifically the "pc-98 look". It retains much of the retro style, but things like dithering, jaggy lines, etc are lacking from it. should be pretty easy to handle and weight. Recommended weight: 0.9-1.

modelVersions.name: PC-98 Light
modelVersions.description:
Light version of the PC98 lora.

Since this is quite a light version of the original, it'd describe it's style more like a "retro look" than specifically the "pc-98 look". It retains much of the retro style, but things like dithering, jaggy lines, etc are lacking from it.

Recommended weight between 0.9-1.

modelVersions.name: PC-98 Medium
modelVersions.description:
A more moderate version of the Lora.

recommended weight between 0.8-1.

modelVersions.name: PC-98 Strong
modelVersions.description:
This version is the strongest (lighter versions coming soon). There may be some issues with hairstyles (very large hair intakes, oversized bangs, etc) - but most are the result of the strong retro styling these games had.

In addition, there are 2 things you should also keep in mind.

  1. Be vary that the stronger the cfg, the stronger it will emulate the older style. That may potentially cause your image to become overtly "low res". If you encounter such an issue, I'd recommend running some xzy to determine the Lora weight and cfg you will need for your desired result.

  2. Since much of the training data was fed with old/retro images, a sort of "soft censor" was produced as a result (ergo, even if you prompt "nude", you still might need to add additional tokens regarding genitalia and areolae to get the desired result).

items.name: Supergirl Cosplay Outfits Collections
items.description:
Patreon

Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 10

  • Lycoris weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.35

Insutrctions

Those are a Lycoris, to use them you need to install the proper extension on Stable Diffusion.

My advice is to start from the prompt of the posted images on civitai, or in any case use most of the keywords with 1.2-1.3 weight.

In general if you want a classic supergirl outfit you just need to use the keyword "wearing supergirl_cosplay_outfit" maybe with a weight if necessary.

If you want a mix like supergirl|ballet or supergirl|bunnyyou should use both keywords, in this cases i have an important advice, play with weights! mostly when adding a particular color to the outfit. I make you an example, most of the training ballet dress images are white, most of the training supergirl outfits are blue, so if you write "(wearing ballet dress with tutu, wearing white supergirl_cosplay_outfit:1.3)" SD will probably generate a normal white ballet dress, so in this case it's better to lower the weight for the ballet dress to have the mix you want, like "(wearing ballet dress with tutu:1.1), (wearing white supergirl_cosplay_outfit:1.3)". Opposite case if you want a blue supergirl ballet outfit.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians

I'm doing this for fun and not for commercial motive, My main purpose is to compose a fictional character using AI with the beauty of all persons above, please support them if you love their works. i do not support any indecent images generated of all persons in this model, I do not support selling generated images of persons in this model. please refrain to what they have been posting online.

All persons in this models are 21+ and not a minor, please DO NOT post explicit nudity, suggestive content, or pornographic content online using this model. Refer to CivitAi TOS for more details.

===

Request or Suggestion Rule:

  1. No request of minor!

  2. The requested should have public data (no private)

  3. Should have more than 30 good quality images

  4. Since all requests or suggestion are free, I will still need to like your request, otherwise its a work not a hobby for me.

  5. Be a decent human being and leave a review if your requests is up It takes you only 5 mins while it takes me hours, electricity, and efforts to do your requests.

  6. If you don't get what you want, do not review bomb, there could be other creators models or lora that can get better results than mine, use theirs instead, and leave a good review on them too, support any other creators for their hardworks!

NOTE : I will keep updating more actresses in versions update

===

Usage Guide

--

A. Lora Weight

  • 0.1 ~ 0.4 -- is to combine multiple faces or features, or if you experience overbaking

  • 0.5 ~ 0.7 -- is a balanced weight to get still accurate feature but with more flexiblity

  • 0.8 ~ 1.0 -- is to create accurate representation of the features.

B. CFG Scale

  • Lower CFG Scale means AI gets more creative and less overbaking problems.

  • Higher CFG Scale means results get very accurate with training sets and more prone to overbaking problems.

  • Dynamic CFG Threshold, using this method allows you to bump up quality and achieve photorealistic easily, but with lycoris i found out recently that this method actually lower success rate, so only use when you are composing with a Lora / model that works fine with this method.

C. Sampling Steps, High Res Fix & Upscaling

  • I like to use sampling steps at 50, with high res step at 20, or 1/2 of sampling steps.

  • I find that 2M Karras works better and faster than SDE Karras. with ERSGAN 4x+ method + ERSGAN 4x for Upscaling. This method actually gives quite good result without being too sharp or too plasticky

  • Upscaling - GPFGAN @0.25, Codeformer @0.3 & Codeformer Weight @0.15 seems to yield superior results to me.

--

Combining with Attribute LoRa / LyCoris

You may need to do your own testing, but using character at weight -0.2 below attribute lora weight yields superior results, if for some reason one features persists not showing or overbake, you may want to lower the weight of the overbaked feature Lora, and then use emphasis () to boost the specific attribute you want.

DDetailer / ADetailer Script

If subject face is small / far away use: DDetailer Script with bbox anime face with default settings except denoiser at 0.2-0.3. You can combine this LoRa with a lot of other Style / Attire / Pose / Acts LoRa, Also works well with character LyCoris.

How to install this script? I kinda forget how because its a bit complicated beacuse you need to install stuff from venv. but a quick google search will land you somewhere in tutorial page.

Enjoy.

💡Workflow Advice💡

🔧Prompt and Sampling🔧

  • What's the + for?

    • Just an easy way to indicate the dataset image for this particular LORA was based off a minimum of 1024px+ quality source images with the LORA trained at 1024,1024 (I may go higher in the future if I can get a properly working configuration).

    • For the most part, you can start with higher base resolutions to capture more details and/or generate higher quality outputs. See some of the gallery examples.

    • You don't have to gen at high resolution, low res generations will be better quality as well.

  • Most images have been generated with LORA weighted @ .75 - 1.

  • For photoreal shots, I've found sampling steps best well above 50 give better results.

  • ControlNet is your friend. Embrace the dark side.😈

    • Tile pre-sample and model is good for extreme close up

items.name: Water Realflow
items.description:
简介 Introduction

这个模型的出发点并不是取代产品图渲染，而是为了还原一些特效广告中的真实水流环绕特效。经过测试，意外发现在二次元模型下调低本模型权重可以获得一些意想不到的效果，例如水中女孩。如果你要支持我，可以通过微信（Anson_NgAu）联系我，让我有电费可以继续跑图训练。

The purpose of this model is not to replace product image rendering, but to recreate realistic water flow effects found in certain special effects advertisements. Surprisingly, through testing, it has been discovered that lowering the weights of this model when combined with a cartoon-style model can yield unexpected results, such as a girl in water. If you would like to support me, you can contact me via WeChat (Anson_NgAu) to contribute towards my electricity expenses for continued training.

请注意，你下载的模型名字和我示例图中的prompts不一样，写prompts时请检查确保名字正确，并记得加上触发词“realflow”!!!

Please note that the name of the model you downloaded may be different from the prompts shown in my example. When writing prompts, please double-check to ensure the correct name and remember to include the trigger word "realflow"!!!

本模型训练时已抹除品牌标签，但需注意的是，产品外形极度相似仍有可能构成侵权嫌疑。如果你用于商用途径，确保使用你自己的产品图作为基础。你可以结合controlnet的reference、图生图或inpainting等功能尽情玩耍！

This model has been trained with brand labels removed. However, it is important to note that if the product design is extremely similar, there is still a possibility of copyright infringement. If you intend to use it for commercial purposes, make sure to use your own product images as a basis. Feel free to explore the functionalities of ControlNet's reference, i2i, or inpainting for added creativity and experimentation!

使用方法：

  • 建议使用chilloutmix生成实物图，权重一般0.6-0.75为宜，不超过0.8（AnythingV3或V5生成水中女孩，权重0.3-0.5）

  • 可以不加花的关键词，或在负面prompts加上“花”，从而只画瓶子和水流

  • 步数建议20-30，采样器使用DPM++ SDE Karras

  • 在512*512，768*768，512*768，768*512可以获得较好效果。不建议开启高清修复！

  • 可以在关键词分别指定背景、瓶子、花的颜色（不常见的颜色可能会造成颜色污染），建议结合xyz图表，改变权重来获得你满意的颜色效果

  • 可以尝试不同关键词来影响瓶子的形状，例如“面霜”、“水瓶”

  • 希望你们能喜欢，并支持我的作品！！！

  • 欢迎评论你使用该模型生成的作品，如果你发现配合哪些其他大模型有更好的效果，请一定不要吝啬，尽管分享！！！

Usage:

  • It is recommended to use "chilloutmix" to generate realistic images, with weights generally ranging from 0.6 to 0.75, but not exceeding 0.8. (For generating a girl in water, you can use "AnythingV3" or "V5" with weights ranging from 0.3 to 0.5.)

  • You can omit specific keyword (flower) or add the word "flower" in negative prompts to focus on drawing only the bottle and water flow.

  • It is suggested to use 20-30 steps with the DPM++ SDE Karras sampler.

  • Good results can be achieved with image sizes of 512x512, 768x768, 512x768, or 768x512. It is not recommended to enable high-resolution refinement.

  • You can specify colors for the background, bottle, and flowers using keywords. However, be aware that using uncommon colors may result in color contamination. It is recommended to consult the XYZ chart and adjust weights to achieve your desired color effects.

  • You can experiment with different keywords to influence the shape of the bottle, such as "face cream" or "water bottle."

  • I hope you enjoy using the model and support my work!!!

  • Feel free to share your generated artwork and provide feedback. If you discover better results by combining this model with other large models, please don't hesitate to share your findings!!!

关于训练：

  • 本模型使用了320张实拍图、处理后的广告图进行训练，尺寸包括512*512，512*768，768*512。并设置了“水”和“瓶子”的reg图集。

  • 这个训练基本上是体力活，90%的时间都是在处理素材，选择好看的瓶子照片很重要。

  • 希望能借此机会抛砖引玉，促成更多此类模型，最终真正帮助可商用的广告设计。

Regarding the training:

  • This model was trained using 320 captured photos and processed advertisement images. The image sizes included 512x512, 512x768, and 768x512. A dedicated REG dataset was created for "water" and "bottle" reference images.

  • Training this model was primarily a labor-intensive task, with approximately 90% of the time spent on processing the materials. Choosing visually appealing bottle photos was crucial.

items.name: Hypernet Henry Cavill 18k Ultimate
items.description:
This is the ultimate Hypernetwork for Henry Cavill with 18k steps, 160 images. This Hypernet designed to be flexible and mixed into prompts instead of having a dedicated checkpoint.

***Remember to adjust the weight of the hypernet from 1 downwards (at max 0.30 and as low as 0.10) if you see artifacts/issues. If you use "RESTORE FACES" option, it will automatically turn Henry's eyes black. I prefer to not use this feature for this, but if you must use it, then you'll need to add "(light blue eyes)" or gray eyes to the prompt perhaps with heavy weight to emphasize the color eyes.***

RECOMMENDED SETTINGS SD 1.5:

Steps: 60

CFG: 3

Prompt Trigger Words: "<hypernet:hyper1-5hnry-18000:0.25> a photo of henry cavill "

Tip#1: Try to use the above Steps and CFG settings first and tweak from there. I think 50 steps may be the minimum acceptable quality. CFG 3 is minimum and after 5, will be a hit or a miss. But you can try other settings to fit your needs.

Tip#2: Using prompt "a luxury modern interior design" works best to trigger the look, then add your own prompt to spice up the picture! Remember to adjust weights as needed!

As a favor, please let me know your thoughts, feedback and give a review rating. I would truly appreciate it!

I've been experimenting with pig's blood cake.

This is my first attempt to train with a new underlying model.

The results are acceptable, and there are unexpected gains.

Previously, when training with meat, I found that the AI could only draw chunks of meat like steak.

It couldn't generate the shredded meat found in Chinese stir-fry dishes. Then, when I applied the pig's blood cake model... oh my, shredded meat appeared...

When placed in soups, the model could better simulate the original form. Anything related to meat will replace the meat...

The suggested weight setting is 0.7~0.85

items.name: Meno Ziriath - Artist Style (LoRA/Lycoris)
items.description:
If you enjoyed this model, why don't you check out my other works? I put a lot of effort into correctly recreating artist styles and making the occasional character LoRA.😊

This model was trained using the collab/guide by holostrawberry [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free - colabs | Stable Diffusion Other | Civitai

About the artist:

Twitter: Meno Ziriath🔞🏳️‍🌈 (@Menoziriath) / Twitter

Patreon: Menoziriath | creating Adult art | Patreon

Meno Ziriath makes nsfw art which consequently results in an nsfw model.

Weights & Prompts

Lycoris:

This should be your goto model for most checkpoints, allowing for more flexibility.

Use a weight of 1.0, adjust to taste. For reference check the XYZ plot in the examples.

LoRA:

Use a weight of 1.0. Go a bit lower (I used 0.75) for character loras. As usual I have included XYZ plots for reference.

For backgrounds and landscapes the model is generally low on details or blurs the background entirely. It results in warmer colors, often increasing the impact of orange components. I have attached one set of landscape images with and without the model.

Please leave a review if you enjoyed this model or have problems with it. This helps me with improving future models and finetuning them in general. Give it a try and throw some images down below! 👇

items.name: Arima Kana [Oshi No Ko] / 有馬加奈【推しの子】/ 有马加奈（帽子）【我推的孩子】
items.description:
[English/中文]

This is my first LoRA model and there had been 7 previous version trained before the fromal version was released. It will be highly appreciated if you could offer me any advice!

Basic Information

Trigger word: arima kana \(oshi no ko\)

Training model: Anything V5 PrtRE (I suggest you use the same model to generate images)

Recommended weight: 0.8-1.0

Example Image Introduction

The relatively extensive datasets enable more elements to be changeable. You'd better look at example images for proper prompts. The example images (originally 600 * 900 definition, 2x SD upsale) are based on Anything V5 PrtRE and AnimeVAE. I don't use any extension except EasyNegativeV2. The same basic parameters will produce the same result.

1-2.       high school uniform (Unfortunately, it is hard for AI to learn to the fact that there is a black bowtie on the back of Kana’s head)

3-5.       a few sets of clothes appeared in the Oshi No Ko anime (not 100% similar)

6-8.       different expressions (I have to admit that the model has quite limited expressions)

9-11.      different angles and poses using Controlnet Openpose (When Openpose is used, the result will be less authentic)

12-13.     other types of clothes

14-16.   greyscale style and other checkpoint models (Obviously, other checkpoint models are less effective than Anything V5 PrtRE)

17.          NSFW (What, do you say that Arima Kana only has small breasts?)

Author’s Words (you can skip it)

Arima Kana is a special girl. She has her particular temperament. So I want to produce a LoRA that can paint Arima Kana, not someone who barely has short red hair, bangs and red eyes. It is a quite challengeable task which few present LoRAs (uploaded in CivitAI) can complete.  I spent a lot of time painstakingly selecting qualified datasets to achieve this goal.

Acknowledgement

I would be glad if you can like the model. Don’t forget to support me!

Finally but most importantly, Arima Kana is the best!

这是我训练的第一个LoRA模型，在最终版本之前已经迭代过7个版本了......欢迎提出宝贵的意见！

基本信息

触发词：arima kana \(oshi no ko\)

训练底模：Anything V5 PrtRE（我建议也用这个模型生成图片）

推荐权重：0.8-1.0

例图介绍

得益于比较多样的训练集，模型产出的图片也将更具多样性。你可以去参考例图的提示词来实现这些效果。例图原始分辨率为600*900，用了2倍的SD放大，底模Anything V5 PrtRE，使用AnimeVAE，并且除了EasyNegativeV2没有使用任何其他额外拓展。相同的基本参数即可产出与例图一样的图片。

1-2.        高中校服（然而AI其实很难意识到加奈后脑勺还有个蝴蝶结）

3-5.        一些在推子动漫出现过的服饰（没办法完全复刻）

6-8.        不同的表情（我承认这个模型的表情并不是很丰富）

9-11.      用Controlnet Openpose产出的不同角度与姿势（Openpose会导致较低的还原度）

12-13.     其他服饰

14-16.     黑白风格和其它大模型（显然，其他模型的产出效果不如Anything V5 PrtRE）

17.          懂的都懂（什么，你想说帽子没那么大？）

作者的话（可跳过）

有马加奈是一个特别的女孩，有着自己的气质。我希望我做的LoRA可以画出那个特别的有马加奈，而不是随便一个有着红色短发、齐刘海、红瞳的人。这个要求非常难实现，目前的C站上加奈的LoRA都很难做到这点。为此我花了很多时间精心挑选数据集以最大程度还原她的特征。

鸣谢

如果你能喜欢这个模型，那就太好啦，同时也别忘了支持我一下噢~

最后但最重要的是，帽子最高！

Karasu Chan - Artist Style 🎨

This LoRA is trained on the unique artstyle of Karasu Chan , known for their artworks about monster girls, you can checkout their creations on PixivFanbox or Pixiv or Twitter [contains explicit content].

-style mentioned by @ComradePedro-

Usage Tips :

  • regular use is at the weight of 0.8 to 1.1

  • No need for activation word but adding karasuchanto the prompt will force the image elements toward subjects (NSFW) covered by the artist , and also gives the LoRA a bit more influence but might break other LoRAs.

  • the LoRA is made to be flexible to work well with color ranges and detail levels, BUT if you're interested in the stylized approach of the artist u can add monochrome or sketch or both 😋

    • if you like that faint color glow that the artist has in most of his sketch you can use {color of your choice}+taint example: monochrome, red taint

Fun Tips :

  • try exploring extreme expressions like evil grin crazy laugh extreme anger envy

  • loves to show teeth so try fangs , shark teeth, clenched teeth

  • mix and mash monster parts like horns , lizard tail, tentacle arms, spider arms . . etc, and see what you can create 😋

Samples settings :

  • Checkpoints: Anything V4.5, A-Zovya RPG Artist Tools V2

  • Steps : 24-26

  • Sampler : DPM++ 2M

  • ClipSkip : 2

have fun and consider rating ⭐
